{"tid":2515502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有片 - 現代教育董事范X偉律師酒吧打交爭女：X你老母，地產仔","createTime":"2021-05-04T04:49:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T04:49:52.000Z","uid":255274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1a6972e821fa7c77c6c3553a16b89bf75ffdd7de","tid":2515502,"uid":255274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T04:49:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OWCpcJFWAts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOWCpcJFWAts&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGno429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=9dfa483a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OWCpcJFWAts</a><br />\n<br />\n佢係知名呃了唔少藝人，包括謝安琪、江美儀和洪金寶比華利山老千黎偉業Michael Lai的法律顧問拍擋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_779650_0/%E6%AF%94%E8%8F%AF%E5%88%A9%E5%B1%B1%E6%98%8E%E6%98%9F%E7%AB%87-%E8%AC%9D%E5%AE%89%E7%90%AA%E6%B1%9F%E7%BE%8E%E5%84%80%E8%A2%AB%E6%93%BA%E4%B8%8A%E6%AA%AF-%E8%B8%A2%E7%88%86%E9%95%B7%E9%AB%AE%E8%80%81%E5%8D%83-%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6%E5%A2%B3%E5%A0%B4-%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC%E9%A8%99%E5%B1%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_779650_0%2F%25E6%25AF%2594%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2598%259F%25E7%25AB%2587-%25E8%25AC%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E7%2590%25AA%25E6%25B1%259F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2584%2580%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2593%25BA%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25AA%25AF-%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E7%2588%2586%25E9%2595%25B7%25E9%25AB%25AE%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%258D%2583-%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25A2%25B3%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E5%258D%2583%25E8%2590%25AC%25E9%25A8%2599%25E5%25B1%2580&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGno429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=2fcb6d5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_779650_0%2F%25E6%25AF%2594%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2598%259F%25E7%25AB%2587-%25E8%25AC%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E7%2590%25AA%25E6%25B1%259F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2584%2580%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2593%25BA%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25AA%25AF-%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E7%2588%2586%25E9%2595%25B7%25E9%25AB%25AE%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%258D%2583-%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25A2%25B3%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E5%258D%2583%25E8%2590%25AC%25E9%25A8%2599%25E5%25B1%2580&h=b8ec0ee3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_779650_0/%E6%AF%94%E8%8F%AF%E5%88%A9%E5%B1%B1%E6%98%8E%E6%98%9F%E7%AB%87-%E8%AC%9D%E5%AE%89%E7%90%AA%E6%B1%9F%E7%BE%8E%E5%84%80%E8%A2%AB%E6%93%BA%E4%B8%8A%E6%AA%AF-%E8%B8%A2%E7%88%86%E9%95%B7%E9%AB%AE%E8%80%81%E5%8D%83-%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6%E5%A2%B3%E5%A0%B4-%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC%E9%A8%99%E5%B1%80</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeKxuy3vja4GWxeoX8eLdNmN9cPoB83bx92HPBwNdeETr?filename=4M9c9ak.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4M9c9ak.jpg&h=0facf2f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢係政府的人，同藍絲有無數關係<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZT5QNxtYaykAXbPm6bD2BP9X3tgXg2QdfbBh89YLAH3Y?filename=UgCqKJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUgCqKJM.jpg&h=62b987ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW1hPKxgeeQmFjDUn2kGjvtunW3rzxE51wy6Xj84SfMwf?filename=9fpTTB6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9fpTTB6.jpg&h=113c72b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢仲教人上市，上面個潘啟才係搞加密貨幣挖礦機呃人，同CY好friend的老千<br />\n<br />\n//被指誤導苦主購買比特幣礦機的潘啟才和袁曉桐均為財經界名人，潘更曾與前特首梁振英共事。袁則是收取買機款項的公司唯一股東及董事，他向《蘋果》承認是售賣礦機的中介。<br />\n <br />\n一批苦主在潘與袁主講的分享會後，即場與賣方Fifth Elements Limited簽約，購買比特幣礦機。公司註冊處資料顯示，該公司的唯一股東及董事是劉承彥，曾有份撰寫《虛幣實戰》一書。《蘋果》昨未能聯絡劉本人。<br />\n <br />\n有苦主稱事後打算追討責任時，潘向他們表示自己與袁都不能代表賣方，「但喺分享會上令到我哋以為間公司同佢哋有關」，而買賣合約上指定轉賬戶口為另一家公司倍升控股，則由袁持有。有苦主嘆謂：「咁樣係金蟬脫殼，講到好似唔關自己事咁。」//<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20180724/IZJKLPZNIHJX4WFH3AAZ6VFD3I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20180724%2FIZJKLPZNIHJX4WFH3AAZ6VFD3I%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGno429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=e37f41a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20180724%2FIZJKLPZNIHJX4WFH3AAZ6VFD3I%2F&h=64019d12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20180724/IZJKLPZNIHJX4WFH3AAZ6VFD3I/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSPkdVKSuGrkFqrpuxEr4ExCocbMGy9JdXwE6fxz9XgV9?filename=qsYhAQx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqsYhAQx.jpg&h=05c152cf&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}